-- Changsha Zoomlion Says Controlling Shareholder Increases Stake by 0.21%
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-19T12:14:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/changsha-zoomlion-says-controlling-shareholder-increases-stake-by-0-21-.html

          
          
             Changsha Zoomlion Heavy Industry
Science and Technology Development Co. said its controlling
shareholder, the Hunan branch of the State-owned Assets
Supervision and Administration Commission, bought 4.2 million,
shares, or 0.21 percent of the outstanding shares, from July 12
to July 16.                                                   
 The purchase is part of a plan by the controlling
shareholder to increase its holding over a six-month period by
as much as 1 percent, according to a statement to Shenzhenâ€™s
stock exchange today.  
